  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Pangomm</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Pangomm</application> package provides a C++
      interface to <application>Pango</application>. This version is part of a
      new API for supporting gtkmm-4.
    </para>

    &lfs122_checked;

